{"hash":"c172d95f3caedc458b15c41bd34a3ceddae884e7","data":{"metadata":{"siteName":"只是玩玩 | JUST FUN","siteDescription":"/gridsome-blog"},"post":{"id":"63158312cf533d1c2cf29b01","title":"英 雄 不 朽 。","content":"<blockquote>3月30日18时许，大凉山深处——凉山州木里县雅砻江镇立尔村发生森林火灾。数百名民兵、消防人员、当地打火队队员等扑向火海，与火魔展开殊死搏斗。着火点位于海拔3800米左右，火场平均海拔达4000米，多个火点位于悬崖峭壁上。3月31日下午，扑火人员在转场途中，受瞬间风力风向突变影响，突遇山火爆燃，30名扑火人员壮烈牺牲。灾情发生后，前线指挥部和后方应急协调组共17个工作组制定实施方案并全力展开工作。截至4月2日零时记者发稿时，大火仍未扑灭。</blockquote><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://cdn.1900.live/20190428/1554185540152.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\"></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://cdn.1900.live/20190459/1554185540468.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\"></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://cdn.1900.live/20190458/1554186327269.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\"></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://cdn.1900.live/20190468/1554186330829.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\"></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://cdn.1900.live/20190451/1554186332875.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\"></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://cdn.1900.live/20190431/1554186334887.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\"></figure>","date":"2 April 2019","path":"heroes-never-die"}},"context":{}}